modShortDescription: Increases the amount of damage a zombie takes when you run it over. Amount of damage depends on how heavy the vehicle is and how fast you hit the zombie.
modDescription:
Increases the amount of damage a zombie takes when you run it over. Amount of damage depends on how heavy the [vehicle](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-vehicles/) is and how fast you hit the zombie.

This is a C# Mod (cannot be server only, EAC must be off!).
